title.rendered: 290 Private Label Sourcing from China in Detail

content.rendered:
Podcast: Play in new window | Download (Duration: 37:44 — 34.5MB)

Subscribe: Spotify | Email | RSS

Sourcing great products is clearly vital for a physical product based business.

In this episode, Michael covers some critical details  including:

  • How to avoid Alibaba Overwhelm
  • The open “secret” to really negotiating well
  • The critical step you need dealing with Chinese suppliers – skip this and it all melts down for you! Links mentioned:

 

Private Label Process (overview and pre-order offer info)

Our Free 4-part Video overview of Amazon business building:

Private Label Class

Watch Private Label Sourcing from China in Detail
